---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="detail-page">
		<div class="back-button">
			<a href="/">← 返回首页</a>
		</div>

		<!-- 教育经历 -->
		<section class="content-section">
			<h2 class="section-title">
				<span class="icon">🎓</span>
				教育经历
			</h2>
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
				<div class="timeline-content">
					<div class="time-period">2023.09 - 2027.07</div>
					<h3>首都体育学院</h3>
					<p class="position">体育经济与管理 | 本科</p>
					<div class="details">
						<p><strong>GPA：</strong>4.0（前 5%）</p>
						<p><strong>荣誉奖项：</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>首都体育学院校级优秀班干部（2 次）</li>
							<li>首都体育学院二等奖学金（2 次）</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 实习经历 -->
		<section class="content-section">
			<h2 class="section-title">
				<span class="icon">💼</span>
				实习经历
			</h2>

			<!-- 新浪微博 -->
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
				<div class="timeline-content">
					<div class="time-period">2026.02 - 至今</div>
					<h3>新浪微博</h3>
					<p class="position">内容运营 | 互联网</p>
					<div class="details">
						<h4>达人孵化与社群生态运营</h4>
						<p>负责领域顶尖达人运营与社群维系。甄选优质 UGC 内容进行定向推荐与流量扶持，通过社群高效分发活动 Brief，调动站内 KOL/KOC 的创作积极性，有效拉动平台内容产出与整体流量增长。</p>

						<h4>热点追踪与资源位分发</h4>
						<p>实时敏锐捕捉全网及站内当日热点趋势，精准筛选潜力话题。结合平台用户画像与内容调性，统筹完成核心资源位的配置与内容推送，最大化提升智搜话题页曝光效率与点击转化。</p>

						<h4>活动落地与创意物料统筹</h4>
						<p>参与线上活动的落地执行，负责海报、宣发文案等多元化创意物料的策划与制作。严格把控项目执行节点，确保活动按计划高质量交付，有效达成话题声量、内容曝光的提升。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 太合音乐集团 -->
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
				<div class="timeline-content">
					<div class="time-period">2025.07 - 2026.02</div>
					<h3>太合音乐集团-秀动</h3>
					<p class="position">赛事运营 | 互联网</p>
					<div class="details">
						<h4>全矩阵宣发内容创作与现场执行</h4>
						<p>负责秀动 App 站内及官方社媒矩阵的宣发内容生产。针对垂直受众，累计策划并输出 20+ 项目的开票文案、Push 弹窗、站内信及核心资源位视觉描述。通过精准的话术迭代，显著提升宣发内容的点击率与用户互动率。项目期现场捕捉现场高光时刻与观众互动素材，通过线上线下联动提升项目的长尾话题度与品牌口碑。</p>

						<h4>策略化用户触达与票务统筹</h4>
						<p>负责项目前期票务规划与分销渠道的内容对齐与结算支持。确保分票逻辑的准确性。利用平台用户画像标签，执行差异化的短信及定向推送计划。通过分析潜在观众偏好，协同实现了多项目的高转化率入场。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 优享嘉诚 -->
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
				<div class="timeline-content">
					<div class="time-period">2025.04 - 2025.06</div>
					<h3>优享嘉诚(北京)文化发展有限公司</h3>
					<p class="position">内容运营 | 文娱</p>
					<div class="details">
						<h4>创作者运营</h4>
						<p>负责执行多个戏剧项目 KOL/KOC 外联计划，精准筛选并邀请小红书、抖音等垂直领域达人深度观演。通过建立高频互动的达人矩阵，产出多维度优质内容，成功推动剧目在购票平台的评分攀升至 9.7 分。</p>

						<h4>节点活动策划运营</h4>
						<p>协同团队针对关键营销节点进行创意策划，成功落地"五一特别祈福"、"汉服主题专场"等多场线下运营活动。通过场景化互动设计增强观众沉浸感，实现活动期间购票转化率提升 10%，有效拉动了票房增长。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 国际滑联 -->
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
				<div class="timeline-content">
					<div class="time-period">2024.10 - 2024.12</div>
					<h3>国际滑联短道速滑世界杯北京站</h3>
					<p class="position">项目运营 | 体育</p>
					<div class="details">
						<h4>平台侧推广运营及热点数据分析</h4>
						<p>根据赛事各阶段节奏，制定并执行了跨平台的差异化推广策略。通过体育达人联动及开屏资源位争取，提升赛事曝光量。结合监控全网舆情与传播数据，分析观众兴趣点。确保赛事热度持续处于高位。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

	* {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	body {
		background: url('/background.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
		background-size: cover;
		font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
		color: #333;
		position: relative;
	}

	body::before {
		content: '';
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		z-index: -1;
	}

	.detail-page {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.back-button {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.back-button a {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: #4a90e2;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.back-button a:hover {
		background: rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.1);
		transform: translateX(-5px);
	}

	.detail-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.detail-header h1 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: #666;
	}

	.content-section {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.4rem;
	}

	.section-title .icon {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
	}

	.timeline-item:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.timeline-dot {
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0.3rem;
		width: 14px;
		height: 14px;
		background: #4a90e2;
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.2);
	}

	.timeline-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 6px;
		top: 1.5rem;
		bottom: -2rem;
		width: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #4a90e2, rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.2));
	}

	.timeline-item:last-child::before {
		display: none;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		background: white;
		padding: 1.2rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.timeline-content:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
		transform: translateX(5px);
	}

	.time-period {
		color: #4a90e2;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
	}

	.timeline-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}

	.position {
		color: #666;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.details {
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.details h4 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2c3e50;
		margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.details h4:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.details p {
		color: #555;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
	}

	.details strong {
		color: #2c3e50;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.details ul {
		margin-left: 1.5rem;
		color: #555;
	}

	.details li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	/* 响应式设计 */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.detail-page {
			padding: 1rem;
		}

		.detail-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.timeline-item {
			padding-left: 2rem;
		}

		.timeline-content {
			padding: 1.2rem;
		}

		.timeline-content h3 {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
